{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un rangi / juhfu Azzis reds/ un manna Brahta Benja- mina Azzis/ ka manna Mutte us jums runna.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un paſakajt mannam Tehwam wiſſu mannu Gohdibu Egiptes-Semmê / un wiſſu / ko juhs effat redſejschi / un ſteidſee- tees/ un atweddeet mannu Teh- wu ſchurp.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiſſch ſampahs Ben-jaminain ſawam Brahtam Kaſ- â/ un raudaja / un Benjamins raudaja pee wiſſa Kaſla.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiſſch ſkuhpſtija wiſ- ſus faivus Brahtus/ un rauda- a pahr teem/ un pehz to runnaja viana Brahti ar wiſſu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ta Slawa tappe dau- ſinuta Warauſ Namma / un azzihſs: Jahsepa Brahti irr ahkuſchi / tad patikſe tas Wa- aiun/ un wiſſa Kalpeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Warauſ ſazzija us Jahsepu : Saffi taweem Brah- teem/ darrajt ta/ uſſranjeet us uhſeem Lohpeem/ un no-eita/ ei- ta us Kanâana Semmi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un nemneet juhfu Teh- wu/ un juhfu Saiſmi/ un nahzeet pee man/ tad es jums Egiptes- Semmes Labbunu dohſchn / un uhs ehdiſeet tahs Semmes Trek- annu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tu pawehſi / ſcho dar- rajt/ nemneet no Egiptes-Sem- mes Rattus preeſch juhfeem Behrnineem/un preeſch juhfahm Seewahm / un weddeet juhfu Tehwu / un nahzeet.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ne noschehlojeet juhfu Namina-Rihkus / jo wiſſas Egiptes-Semmes Labbuus jun peederrehs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Ifraëka Dehti darri ja ta/ un Jahſeps dewe teem Rat tus/ pehz Warauſ Wahrdeem un wiſſch dewe teem Zelta-Bar ribu us Zeltu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiſſeem dewe wiſſo ikweenam Swehtku-Drehbes/ un Benjaminain dewe wiſſch trihs ſimts Sudraba Gabbalus/ un peez Swehtku-Drehbes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ſawam Tehwam juh tiſa wiſſch ta patt deſinitis Eh- setus/ kas no to Egiptexu Labbu ma nefſe/ un deſinitis Ehſetu Mahtes/ kas nefſe Labbibu / un Maiſi/ un Barribu preeſch fa wa Tehwa us Zeltu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiſſch noſuhttija fa wus Brahtus/ un tee aſsgahje un wiſſch ſazzija: ne baxxatee wirs Zeltu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee gabje us augſchi no Egiptes-Semmes / un nahz Kanâana Semmê pee Jehfabu fawu Tehwu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ſtabſtija wiſſam/ ſaz zidami: Jahſeps wehl dſihwo un irr weens Walditajs pah wiſſu Egiptes-Semmi. Bet Jeh- kaba Sirde gann zittadi dohma ja/ jo wiſſch teem ne tizzeja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet kad tee us wiſſu runnaja wiſſus Jahsepa Wahr dus/ fo wiſſch us teem bij ſazzijis; un kad wiſſch tohs Rattue erandsija/ fo Jahſeps bij juhttiji\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
